Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯…
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}請…
Dialogue: 2,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那…那就打擾一下了
