Dialogue: 2,0:17:44.50,0:17:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些羨煞旁人的事 對我們來說是重要的交流方式
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.00,0:17:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我才不管這些常識
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.22,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你們倒是讓我也看看那些羨煞旁人的事啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看你個鬼啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小司
Dialogue: 2,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}老公
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那個…
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早安
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.82,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯…早安
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}昨…昨晚真是火熱呢
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不…不是 並沒有到那種地步
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.00,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的 真的啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小司你和她說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早安 千歲
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太陽曬屁股了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哎呀哎呀 今天的睡姿也是如此性感呢
Dialogue: 3,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}千歲 早上啦
Dialogue: 3,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以說你為什麼要把臉貼這麼近啊
Dialogue: 3,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因為你完全不起床啊
Dialogue: 3,0:18:57.03,0:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然後…
Dialogue: 3,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我會起床的 離我遠點
Dialogue: 3,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我來幫你換衣服吧
Dialogue: 3,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}笨蛋笨蛋 你把手往哪伸啊
Dialogue: 3,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我幫你脫衣服哦
Dialogue: 3,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}誰要你幫啊
Dialogue: 3,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}別害羞嘛
Dialogue: 3,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}這並非性騷擾
Dialogue: 3,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}這女僕 只是個天然色
Dialogue: 3,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}話說剛才我聽說了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:19:29.27,0:19:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}星空和小司昨晚好像非常火熱哦
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什麼意思
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不 剛才…
Dialogue: 3,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我去澡堂洗澡的時候
Dialogue: 3,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}碰巧聽到他們在說這些
Dialogue: 3,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你早上還去那裡洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 3,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不…不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 3,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}反…反正他們是夫妻 做這些不是很正常嗎…
Dialogue: 3,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}這些指的是什麼事？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.96,0:20:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}請告訴我他們做了哪些火熱的事
Dialogue: 3,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不不不 又太近了
Dialogue: 3,0:20:04.22,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是在床上牽手擁抱那檔子事啊
Dialogue: 3,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是我平時對千歲做的那些事嗎
Dialogue: 3,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}能不能說人話
Dialogue: 3,0:20:13.65,0:20:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比起那些
Dialogue: 3,0:20:15.98,0:20:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}更加激烈
Dialogue: 3,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}激烈…
Dialogue: 3,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}簡單來說
Dialogue: 3,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是夫妻關係和睦吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是啊
Dialogue: 3,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯嗯 關係和睦是好事
Dialogue: 3,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我和歐羅拉也是關係和睦的好朋友？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算…算是吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那麼
Dialogue: 3,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今晚就牽著手一起睡吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也行…
Dialogue: 3,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}開玩笑的 玩笑玩笑
Dialogue: 3,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那麼 晚安啦
Dialogue: 3,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}魔性的女人
