Dialogue: 3,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}晚安之吻呢
Dialogue: 3,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所…所以說那樣就又會…
